data: Flippity Francine: While trying to achieve a difficult soccer move, called the pinwheel kick, Francine trips and flips while being taped by Muffy. She soon becomes an internet sensation, but grows tired of all the attention. She decides she wants to be famous for something she is proud of and achieves the cartwheel kick in a soccer game against Mighty Mountain. Muffy Takes the Wheel: Muffy and her classmates are excited about the 1st Annual Lakewood Derby. Each student is required to create a racing car from a block of wood. Muffy asks her father for help, but finds that he has taken over the assignment. Rather than using the car that her father made, Muffy creates her own design the night before the race and achieves second place in the derby.
